		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Great lesson. I find that playing just root-five early in the song, backing down for early solos, and then playing more takes the energy level up. I don&#8217;t know if there&#8217;s a lesson on this but if not I&#8217;d love to have one about how changing what you play over the course of a song helps change the feel.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
